{"id": "1487368423947243571", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "レベル60/2凸/緑炎スキルレベル3の弱リッツでもリリーとかのバフ重ねれば1ターンで毒6k蓄積できたんで、普通に強く使えそうでしたよ。", "timestamp": "2026-03-28T08:31:06.238000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1446419399761199114"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1487125552132264158", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1487396903678115962", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "詫び石が大量に配られて石に多少余裕が出きたので､再びパートナーの特訓を完凸するか否かで迷っているのですが､参考にしたいので特訓を取った場合の運用方法や､メリットなどを教えて欲しいです🙏", "timestamp": "2026-03-28T10:24:16.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
