{"id": "1487401152046960691", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォ/24/ジェンキン/リッツ/オレッタ\nが持たせる適性で、持たせてサブ札を火力札にすると、行ける融災難易度が一つ上がるって感じかもしれないです", "timestamp": "2026-03-28T10:41:09.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-28T10:41:38.026000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
